What do back-to-school fashion and instant messaging have to do with one
another?
Not much, but as kids across the States flock back to the classroom
decked out in new fall duds (and what's with this whole "vest" thing,
anyway--will cummerbunds be next?), so returns the big kid on the IM
block sporting a host of new features.
Introducing a new ICQ:
http://www.download.com/DD/dl/0,302,0-0817-1-002,00.html
Now, this is no double-decimal-point update; version 99b beta packs in a
couple new features and other smart improvements that stand to give ICQ a
permanent seat at the head of the instant messaging class.
And one more thing: don't miss all the back-to-school resources in this
week's dispatch. We promise: no vests.
Jim Stanley
Senior producer, CNET Download.com
