Feature: Net Auction Nightmares
In desperate need of a rare Beanie Baby? Just surf to the auction site of
your choice, and chances are you'll find what you're looking for. But if
you start bidding, prepare for the worst: fraud, price fixing, and plain
old bad business. We feature five tales of auction terror, then suggest
the best ways to avoid bidding breakdown.
http://www.download.com/DD/dl/0,302,0-0817-1-035,00.html
First Look: Microsoft FrontPage 2000
Go ahead and call us Bill's toadies, but we don't think you could pick a
smarter WYSIWYG HTML editor than Microsoft FrontPage 2000. It costs a
pretty penny, but you get what you pay for: a smart, sophisticated Web
design program that blows clunky FrontPage 98 out of the water.
http://www.download.com/DD/dl/0,302,0-0817-1-037,00.html
Power Downloader: Summer Movie Madness
This summer's crop of blockbusters has kept Power Downloader mighty busy.
From the black-leather cool of "The Matrix" to the white-knuckle chills
of that indie shocker, "The Blair Witch Project," our hero's been in
