6. Gamecenter's GamerX goes multiplayer after school!
Multiplayer games have sure changed throughout the years and the changes
have definitely been for the better. For most gamers, "the good old days"
meant coming home from school, sitting in front of the Atari 2600, and
playing a challenging game of tank battle with the next door neighbor.
Now we have the option of playing 3D shooters with our battle-buddies in
Japan. To celebrate not doing homework, GamerX has put together a list of
multiplayer favorites stretching from Doom to online Tetris clones. So
put your books down and get ready for battle!
http://www.download.com/DD/dl/0,302,0-0817-1-041,00.html
Don't forget to check out Gamecenter's Online Gaming Guide
http://www.download.com/DD/dl/0,302,0-0817-1-042,00.html
Find all the latest PC games here:
http://www.download.com/DD/dl/0,302,0-0817-1-043,00.html
